reviews.text: Good value with clean, simple and tasty food.  We take the little ones there each weekend. Nothing fancy, but a nice local place for sure.  Lots of variety... we love the vegetable lasagna.
One of the lowest price places to eat in Hong Kong.  For the price it's a good value and food is ok over all for what it is.

Restaurant looks incredibly nice and friendly which I like. Customer service is great. Food on the other hand, could be better. I went there with 6 other friend who all ordered different food and ended up with more or less similiar complains. Some of the food was weirdly served within seconds which questions if it was microwaved.
Best value in Tung Chung, steaks remarkably good and a good selection of Western and other food. Good for families and kids.
